rows.label: qst640202_msg0001
rows.name:
Idaten, that was quick! I hope you
didn't tire yourself out, now.

rows.label: qst640202_msg0002
rows.name:
What, that? No way, it was 
easy-peasy and lots of fun!

rows.label: qst640202_msg0003
rows.name:
What did the customer have to
say, then?

rows.label: qst640202_msg0006
rows.name:
I have a sinking suspicion that the
delivery didn't make it.

rows.label: qst640202_msg0007
rows.name:
Seeing as our delivery specialist has
the remains of some Love Raspberries
on his stomach and around his mouth...

rows.label: qst640202_msg0008
rows.name:
Ah, you mean this here? It's funny
you mention that, now, because 
you'll never believe what happened...

rows.label: qst640202_msg0010
rows.name:
Ahh... Umm... ARGH! It's not my
fault,okay? They just look so good,
they're BEGGING to be eaten!

rows.label: qst640202_msg0011
rows.name:
I mean what else was I gonna do?
Let the desserts down by NOT helping
them to fulfill their destiny? No way!

rows.label: qst640202_msg0012
rows.name:
You've got to be kidding me...
You'll have to go again and have a bit
more self-control this time, Idaten.

rows.label: qst640202_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm sorry! I can do it, really I can! 
I promise, this time I'll be really 
careful and not eat anything!

rows.label: qst640202_msg0014
rows.name:
Okay, then. Let's try again and see
how you get on.

rows.label: qst640202_msg0015
rows.name:
So the delivery was to Ciamran in
Superbia. Got it?

rows.label: qst640202_msg0016
rows.name:
Got it! Just leave it to me. Don't
worry about anything!

rows.label: qst640202_msg0017
rows.name:
All right Idaten. And remember,
no nibbling this time.
